caption:
Need to spice up your next staff meeting? Subway has you covered!

Not only can Subway add flavor to your next shift, Subway is also committed to supporting nurses by providing delicious meal options to keep you fueled and focused during your tireless efforts in caring for others. 

As a heartfelt “thank you” to our amazing nurses during Nurses Week, Subway is giving 40 lucky winners $25 gift cards! 

⭐️ To enter, simply visit the link in bio and enter your email. We’ll randomly select winners the week of 5/12. 

👉 Spread the word and tag a nurse who deserves a treat!

Giveaway is not associated with Meta. Giveaway closes 5/12 2359 EST. Winners will be contacted after the giveaway period closes via email. Winners must be located in the United States and must be 18 years or older at the time of entry. By entering, you agree to The Nursing Beat’s Giveaway Terms & Conditions.
